#. <section class="sutta" id="sn7.14"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn7.14:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.14:0.2"
msgid "2. Upāsakavagga"
msgstr "2. Lay Followers"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn7.14:0.3"
msgid "14. Mahāsālasutta"
msgstr "14. A well-to-do brahmin"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.176"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.378"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.14:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

#. VAR: lūkhapāvuraṇo → lūkhapāpuraṇo (bj, s1-3, km, pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn7.14:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho aññataro brāhmaṇamahāsālo lūkho lūkhapāvuraṇo yena bhagavā "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then a certain well-to-do brahmin, shabby, wearing a shabby cloak, went up "
"to the Buddha, and exchanged greetings with him."

msgctxt "sn7.14:1.3"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinnaṃ kho taṃ brāhmaṇamahāsālaṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one "
"side. The Buddha said to him:"

msgctxt "sn7.14:1.4"
msgid "“kiṃ nu tvaṃ, brāhmaṇa, lūkho lūkhapāvuraṇo”ti?"
msgstr "“Brahmin, why are you so shabby, wearing a shabby cloak?”"

msgctxt "sn7.14:1.5"
msgid "“Idha me, bho gotama, cattāro puttā."
msgstr "“Master Gotama, I have four sons."

msgctxt "sn7.14:1.6"
msgid "Te maṃ dārehi sampuccha gharā nikkhāmentī”ti."
msgstr "At their wives’ bidding they expelled me from my house.”"

msgctxt "sn7.14:1.7"
msgid ""
"“Tena hi tvaṃ, brāhmaṇa, imā gāthāyo pariyāpuṇitvā sabhāyaṃ mahājanakāye "
"sannipatite puttesu ca sannisinnesu bhāsassu:"
msgstr ""
"“Well then, brahmin, memorize these verses and recite them to your sons when "
"you are all seated in the council hall with a large crowd."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.14:2.1"
msgid "‘Yehi jātehi nandissaṃ,"
msgstr "‘I was overjoyed when they were born,"

# This sense of bhava is unusual and not recorded in PTS Dict.
#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.14:2.2"
msgid "yesañca bhavamicchisaṃ;"
msgstr "and wished for them the very best."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.14:2.3"
msgid "Te maṃ dārehi sampuccha,"
msgstr "But at their wives’ bidding they chased me out,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.14:2.4"
msgid "sāva vārenti sūkaraṃ."
msgstr "like hounds after hogs."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.379"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.14:3.1"
msgid "Asantā kira maṃ jammā,"
msgstr "It turns out they’re wicked, those nasty men,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.14:3.2"
msgid "tāta tātāti bhāsare;"
msgstr "though they called me their dear old Dad."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.14:3.3"
msgid "Rakkhasā puttarūpena,"
msgstr "They’re monsters in the shape of sons,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.14:3.4"
msgid "te jahanti vayogataṃ."
msgstr "throwing me out as I’ve grown old."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.14:4.1"
msgid "Assova jiṇṇo nibbhogo,"
msgstr "Like an old, useless horse"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.14:4.2"
msgid "khādanā apanīyati;"
msgstr "led away from its fodder,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.14:4.3"
msgid "Bālakānaṃ pitā thero,"
msgstr "the elderly father of those kids"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.14:4.4"
msgid "parāgāresu bhikkhati."
msgstr "begs for alms at others’ homes."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.14:5.1"
msgid "Daṇḍova kira me seyyo,"
msgstr "Even my staff is better"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.14:5.2"
msgid "yañce puttā anassavā;"
msgstr "than those disobedient sons,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.14:5.3"
msgid "Caṇḍampi goṇaṃ vāreti,"
msgstr "for it wards off a wild bull,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.14:5.4"
msgid "atho caṇḍampi kukkuraṃ."
msgstr "and even a wild dog."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.14:6.1"
msgid "Andhakāre pure hoti,"
msgstr "It goes before me in the dark;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.14:6.2"
msgid "gambhīre gādhamedhati;"
msgstr "in deep waters it supports me."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.14:6.3"
msgid "Daṇḍassa ānubhāvena,"
msgstr "By the wonderful power of this staff,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.14:6.4"
msgid "khalitvā patitiṭṭhatī’”ti."
msgstr "when I stumble, I stand firm again.’”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.14:7.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho so brāhmaṇamahāsālo bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo pariyāpuṇitvā "
"sabhāyaṃ mahājanakāye sannipatite puttesu ca sannisinnesu abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Having memorized those verses in the Buddha’s presence, the brahmin recited "
"them to his sons when they were all seated in the council hall with a large "
"crowd. …"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.380"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
